Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:24.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Podľa chýrov v priemysle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,prvá spoločnosť, ktorá začala vyrábať okuliare,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,objavila techniku,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:32.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ktorá umožňovala zmeniť veci, ktoré si predstavujete na kyberhmotu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:36.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nikto naozaj nevie, ako to dopadlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.07,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Juko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:41.07,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Juko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:43.87,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.75,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíš sem chodiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:49.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.21,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto nie je správna cesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.34,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Nesmieš sem chodiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,4-4-2-3...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si 4-4-2-3, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.97,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Zbohom,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:01.30,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Juko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím sa ťa na niečo spýtať-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:05.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.27,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Auau!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Už zase...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,4-4-2-3...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to znamená?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedávaš do toho dosť energie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Za trest dostaneš ďalších 20 minút!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka, že si prišiel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Podarilo sa mi rozbiť Priestor nášho domu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a tatko sa vážne naštval.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:46.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevráti mi okuliare, pokiaľ nebudem každý deň cvičiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.27,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stretol som Gačagiriho a Namečiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorili, že Isako s nimi trénuje špeciálne techniky okuliarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zobú tej prekliatej Isako z ruky...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je to Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj on je s Gačim a ostatnými?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ktovie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Končene som dorazila matiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz nám zostáva už len voľný výskum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:13.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Počuj...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:17.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vykašlime sa na Harakena a dajme dokopy to, čo sme doteraz zistili.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inak to nikdy nedokončíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To preháňaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezabudni, že je to predovšetkým Harakenov výskum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeme ho len tak ukončiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do konca prázdnin zostáva už len týždeň.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:35.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo nenapíšeme niečo o Bradatých a tej rybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To bude stačiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš, aké sme s tým mali problémy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:43.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak o tom napíšeme, bude z toho ešte väčší malér!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo tak Plesio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,S tým neboli problémy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale on je mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A Denpa nechcel, aby sa o tom niekto dozvedel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoríme tu o počítačovom víruse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Načo sa rozrušovať kvôli nejakému vírusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:03.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto sa kvôli nemu zmenil na oceán sĺz?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:06.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vtedy som sa nechala uniesť atmosférou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okrem toho, skúmanie Ilegálov nie je jediný spôsob
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ako zistiť pravdu o tých nehodách.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zatiaľ nemáme dosť materiálu na referát.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:17.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslela som, že sa nám podarí niečo nájsť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zistila si niečo z Dopravného výboru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.91,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poslala som im mail,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ale povedali mi, že to patrí pod Správu kyberpriestoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak som sa obrátila na Správu Kyberpriestoru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a tí povedali, že je to záležitosť polície.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže si musela kontaktovať políciu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to dopadlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vraj sa mám obrátiť na Dopravný podnik...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Neberú nás vážne, lebo sme decká.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Skočím na záchod.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.48,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{tv}{i dont understand the first line}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.36,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď je v Priestore slabý signál,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.07,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,prejavuje sa ako hustá hmla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.03,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrite sa na toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.45,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Neuveriteľné!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.03,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmla nadobudla podobu malého dievčatka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.37,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Viacerí ľudia dosvedčili,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.49,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,že na tejto križovatke videli čiernu postavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.83,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Postava pripomína smutne sa tváriace dievča.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.54,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to snáď postrach dnešných detí
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.42,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,slávna slečna Mičiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.34,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Čoskoro odhalíme celú pravdu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To je ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To už je toľko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Skoro som zabudla, že sa mám stretnúť s Harakenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okrem toho, Megaba sa ešte nevrátila z nemocnice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.27,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcela som, aby postrážila dom, kým budem preč...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haló?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Daikocká nemocnica?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasako!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám skvelé správy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tá šou...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fumie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve volali z nemocnice! Megaba má veľký problém!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Babička!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Neberte starej žene jej jediné potešenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukrutníci!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorila som vám,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,že v nemocnici nemôžete grilovať!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čakala som, že pôjde o niečo také.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Babička...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje kríže...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje kríže!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.78,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, ale myslím, že pôjdem radšej do čitárne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím čo najskôr dokončiť svoj výskum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľmi sa ospravedlňujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No teda...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako môžeš ísť na návštevu do nemocnice a skončiť ako pacient?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:50.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale aj tak som hlboko sklamaná.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:54.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doktori ani sestry tu nemajú žiadnu úctu k starším.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To kvôli tomu, ako sa správaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:02.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby si vážili, čo všetko tvoj dedko pre túto nemocnicu urobil,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,nepozastavovali by sa nad takou maličkosťou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslela som, že dedko pracoval na vývoji okuliarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby si vedela, v tejto nemocnici tvoj dedko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:15.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,viedol výskum o využití okuliarov na lekárske účely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O tom som nikdy nepočula.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:23.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoj dedko sa zaslúžil o to, aby sa v nemocnici mohli voľne nosiť okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš si predstaviť, ako sa vďaka nemu veci uľahčili?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie som si celkom istá, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,dedko musel byť výnimočný človek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.51,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to teda bol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Babi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:41.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,počula si niečo o 4-4-2-3?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,4-4-2-3?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.15,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Znie to ako nejaké meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nemôžem si spomenúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,čo by to tak mohlo byť?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám to na jazyku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:01.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš, že som pred štyrmi rokmi odpadla a stratila pamäť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Už viem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabudla som si vyzdvihnúť lieky na chrbát!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto si sedela v čakárni!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To je príznak demencie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň s tým!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi nemám na výber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Choď napred a ja ich skočím vybrať.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:31.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa zastaraný Priestor rozširuje len v Daikoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.41,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čau!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne-Nekome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:37.95,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tu robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zajtra sem nastupujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:48.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Požiadala som o posily a oni posielajú podriadených?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.30,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nie som tvoj podriadený.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Som tvoj šéf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Šéf?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som si to, žiadne odkazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.06,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{incomprehensible whispers}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.41,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten hlas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehovorte mi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,že aj tu je zastaraný Priestor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten hlas znie nejako inak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám to, mám to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo máš?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.64,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ale to je...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.27,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Špehovanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozorovanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, neprezraď ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:56.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Netušila som, že tvoje zvieratko vie fotiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Niektoré fotky sú zaujímavé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.95,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepovedz to mojej sestre!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak chceš zachovať moju dôstojnosť, neprezraď ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemal som na výber, ver mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že to ľutuješ,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,tak pre tentokrát ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tu robia moje fotky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si fotil akurát toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To ti nikdy neodpustím!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okamžite to vymaž!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:33.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:36.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...tu v nemocnici?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tá fotka bola spravená len pred chvíľou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isako sa správa podozrivo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Podozrivo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:48.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to len moja domnienka,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:52.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ale myslím si, že kľúč k jej tajomstvu je v tejto nemocnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawino tajomstvo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:59.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekto z jej rodiny tu bol hospitalizovaný.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zistil som, že ho sem chodila navštevovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale aj keď ho už dávno prepustili,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:10.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isako sem stále chodí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno je chorá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:19.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,som presvedčený, že sem chodí na návštevu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:19.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zistil som,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,že chodí do inej izby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do inej izby?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do tej, čo práve vstúpila.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A to je podozrivé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:31.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedá sa do nej vstúpiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je chránená nejakým neznámym kódom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kód v nemocničnej izbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No nie je to podozrivé?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:44.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto som sa pokúsil doňho urobiť otvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeme do tej izby nazrieť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo to urob!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to by bolo „špehovanie“...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:54.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poviem všetko Fumie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inštalujem úpravy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyšlo to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvyšok je už hračka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:16.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To je v pohode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iba sa zmenila doména.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O chvíľu nabehne obraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:26.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,prečo ťa zaujíma Isako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Počuj, Akira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to číslo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to číslo izby, kam vošla Amasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To je ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,4-4-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,2-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.54,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Podľa očitých svedkov,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.58,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,okolie zaplavilo zvláštne svetlo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.83,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,a bolo vidieť niečo, čo pripomínalo prechod.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.42,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom sa objavili čierne postavy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.96,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,a začali mávať akoby na privítanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú to nezmysly, ale celkom zábavné.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.72,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{tv}Snažia sa s nami takto komunikovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimochodom,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,čo si myslel tým „pred štyrmi rokmi“?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:10.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.06,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{tv}a ľudia v blízkosti tej osoby boli prekliati.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.68,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno ich stihne ten istí osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcela som sa ťa na niečo spýtať...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:22.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeme to skopírovať a použiť ako referát?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu je to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Choď bližšie, Micetka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte kúsok...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tentokrát sa mi to podarí.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Už len chvíľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak vydrž.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,4-4-2-3 je...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,číslo izby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.42,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo je Amasawa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:50.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za stenu? Možno je to sterilná miestnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Skúsim sa tam dostať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:58.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Musí to byť stena, ktorá bráni filmovaniu pacienta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže tam niekto je.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:02.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Skúsim to rozkódovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu je!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehýbe sa, ale
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,je nažive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:20.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To snáď...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.25,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vtedy vyzeral byť tak silný...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:26.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidím tvár!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:42.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To, čo robíme
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,nie je správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:47.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.11,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite sa uzdravíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.28,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sa tiež nevzdám.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:55.74,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Maj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Micetka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Odíď spolu s ňou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,je možné, že mal tú istú jazvu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to len náhoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je tá izba?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Na štvrtom poschodí štvrtého bloku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dlho sme sa nevideli.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Naposledy to bolo, keď sa stala tá nehoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zase máš niečo v pláne?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň s tým.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tentokrát som ti prišiel pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomôcť?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:56.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Priviedol som posily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O nijaké posily som nežiadala.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:05.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale tváriš sa, ako by si prijala pomoc aj od mačky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne ako vtedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak ide o kirabugy, zvládnem to sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bystrá, ako vždy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:16.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si sa zase vrátil k tomuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som, že rozšírim oblasť skúmania
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,na všetky nehody spojené s okuliarmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby sme to spravili podľa mňa, mali by sme to dávno z krku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A na čo si prišiel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaujalo ma pár vecí.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu jeden záhadný článok spred štyroch rokov.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:44.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,„Za posledných pár dní sa zvýšil počet detí, čo stratili vedomie.“
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:47.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Našťastie sa všetky deti rýchlo zotavili
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a rýchlo sa na to zabudlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:50.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A príčina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Neznáma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale je tu jedna domnienka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Píše sa tu, že všetky deti, čo odpadli
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,mali na sebe kyberokuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:06.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A aj keď neviem, či je to pravda,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:10.25,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,píše sa tu, že po tom, čo sa deti prebrali, mali zvláštne halucinácie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Halucinácie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:12.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To sa tu nepíše.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že je to čoraz zamotanejšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A ešte tento článok...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Týka sa to tiež okuliarov?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to niečo, čo ma obzvlášť trápi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyberliek?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem o tom veľa,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ale možno to je nejaká stopa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa do toho pustíme, možno niečo objavíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem ďalej hľadať.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokračuje to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:54.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To snáď...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem tam len tak vôjsť...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepomyslel by som si, že ich je toľko druhov...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Beta-typy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takisto ako Alfa-typy pravdepodobne prišli z podzemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ktovie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale je isté, že majú niečo dočinenia s Imágom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A ešte je tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa Juko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keďže nemáme právomoci polície,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,môžeme ju jedine chytiť pri čine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíme počkať, kým nenazbiera všetky kirabugy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by sme zlyhali a dostane sa to na verejnosť,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:55.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hlavná centrála sa sformátuje na úroveň tri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedna vec mi stále nedá pokoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo Isako zbiera kirabugy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To náhodou viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ide o jej brata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak je ten pacient...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.42,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isakin príbuzný, tak potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď som prehľadávala mestské legendy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,našla som niečo zaujímavé!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:25.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to kniha príbehov detí, ktoré pred štyrmi rokmi odpadli.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:29.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú tu aj obrázky, čo nakreslili po prebudení.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Som hlúpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si od toho sľubujem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Spomienka, ktorá je ako sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A takisto to číslo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to náhoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko to bola pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo chceš urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si ma sledovala?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:37.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:39.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mala som sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.30,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...pomohol mi nájsť Densukeho...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:48.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorím nezmysly, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:57.27,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že som ho už stretla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Toho z izby 4-4-2-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:01.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O čo ti ide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako si sa dozvedela o mojom bratovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.25,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bratovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:21.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže 4-4-2-3 je tvoj brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak chceš vedieť, pred štyrmi rokmi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.51,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,keď som bola malá,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,možno som stretla tvojho brata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Č-Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom sa niečo stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:34.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz mi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,čo sa stalo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,s tvojím bratom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:43.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat Juko Amasawy je v kóme?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, už niekoľko rokov.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa chce nazbierať kirabugy a potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kľúčová dierka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A tie ľudské postavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne ako v Kanninom denníku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:02.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Podľa očitých svedkov,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,pretínala zebra kľúčovú dierku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:06.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A aj keď bol večer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:09.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko ožiarovalo zapadajúce slnko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:11.51,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zapadajúce slnko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:14.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno to bola...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:15.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,„druhá strana“...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to naozaj chceš vedieť, poviem ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď mi asi neuveríš.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:25.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Budeš si myslieť, že táram nezmysly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:30.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj brat sa už sem nemôže vrátiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:34.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeho duša aj kybertelo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,sú na „druhej strane“.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:37.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj teraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:39.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,„Druhou stranou“ myslíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,tú, ktorá sa spomína v mestských legendách?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:45.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to predsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:47.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vedela som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:50.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne ako som si myslela,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:53.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,si taká istá ako dospelí.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:56.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:22:59.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,presne ako sa hovorí v mestských legendách.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:01.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Samé nezmysly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:03.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Už sa cítiš lepšie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:06.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokázala si, že som blázon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak si spokojná,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:12.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,už nikdy sa ku mne nepribližuj.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:17.41,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:49.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Dennou Coil:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.38,0:24:52.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Posledné letné prázdniny
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:55.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tešte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.22,0:24:57.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
